蓝牙芯片供应商来偷偷通过。 Valve 侦探 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/SadlyItsBradley/status/1709644205084021226&quot;>;Brad Lynch 和 @TVKilledMi...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T13:00:11-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T13:00:11-04:00</updated><title>三星刚刚将其条形音箱变成了 SmartThings 中心</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;条形音箱和电视。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gUOwf5tIH-xWAmi5DZ4hN7jBrVg=/56x0:653x398/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72724615/2023_Soundbar_HW_Q900C_KV_0 1_PC.5.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;三星最新的条形音箱 HW-Q900C 现在能够成为 SmartThings 中心&lt;/em>; |图片：三星&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;qBSGTA&quot;>;在今天的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.samsungdeveloperconference.com/&quot;>;年度开发者大会&lt;/a>;上，三星再次将其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.smartthings.com/&quot;>;SmartThings 智能家居平台&lt;/a>;放在首位，宣布其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://news.samsung.com/us /samsung-introduces-new-premium-soundbar-lineup-2023/&quot;>;最新条形音箱 HW-Q900C&lt;/a>; 现在能够成为 SmartThings 中心，并支持 Zigbee，&lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/23165855/thread-smart-home-protocol-matter-apple-google-interview&quot;>;主题&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 22787729/matter-smart-home-standard-apple-amazon-google&quot;>;事情&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;eJ0DMZ&quot;>;这家电子巨头在过去几年中一直在积极推动 SmartThings，致力于连接来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ 的所有电器、电视、智能手机和小工具。 /www.theverge.com/2023/8/29/23850250/samsung-lg-app-home-connectivity-alliance-appliances-ifa&quot;>;其他制造商&lt;/a>;一起构建基于物联网的统一智能家居生态系统。在其 &lt;a 